sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant ActivityController
    participant ActivityService
    participant GetActivityUseCase
    participant Repository

    Client->>ActivityController: GET /activities/{id}
    ActivityController->>ActivityService: getActivity(id)
    ActivityService->>GetActivityUseCase: execute(id)
    GetActivityUseCase->>Repository: findById(id)
    Repository-->>GetActivityUseCase: activity
    GetActivityUseCase-->>ActivityService: activity
    ActivityService-->>ActivityController: activity
    ActivityController-->>Client: ResponseEntity(activity)
